# - ADX: 22.01 (DEVELOPING - below 25 threshold)
# - Status: ADX needs to climb above 25 for strong trend
# - LOD: ~$1.50 | Recent high: $2.10
# - Catalyst: 20% stake in KWeather for $4.3M
#
# STRATEGY:
# Wait for ADX to confirm trend strength (>22 lowered threshold due to
# current ADX at 22.01). Needs +DI > -DI for bullish direction.
